Our general approach is modified MYO armband for hand motion classification using capacitive surface electromyography EMG
electrodes, we intended to manufacture a 3D-printed prosthetic hand designed by hand project company, dc motors with a
self-lock for fingers motion,Raspberry PI and MYO armband . We used Python programming language . and my roll is controlling
the 5 dc motors and servo motor , configuration the raspberry pi and assembling the mechanical parts.
